Combine SMUCKER'S(R) preserves, vinegar, garlic salt, ginger, soy sauce and crushed red pepper flakes; stir until well blended. Set aside. Heat 2 tablespoons oil in wok or large skillet until hot. Stir-fry zucchini and mushrooms over medium-high heat until zucchini is crisp-tender. Transfer mixture to a platter. Add remaining oil to wok; cook chicken until tender, stirring often. Add pea pods and cooked zucchini and mushrooms; toss gently to mix well and heat through. Pour apricot sauce over chicken and vegetables; toss gently to mix well and heat through. Serve with rice, if desired.